Subsequently, an application under Order XII Rule 6 read with Order VII Rule 11 of the CPC was filed on behalf of the respondent in which the following prayers were made:-
"In view of the admitted facts, it is humbly prayed that this Hon'ble Court, may kindly be pleased to:
i. pass an order under Order VII Rule 11 of CPC dismissing/rejecting the counter-claim bearing CS(COMM) No. 58 of 2023;
ii. pass a judgment under Order XII Rule 6 of CPC in favour of the Respondents;
iii. award costs in the Respondents; and iv. pass any such other and further Orders as this Hon'ble Court may deem fit in the interest of justice."
